eering,IIT Bombay |\n| Sh. Vikram Shroff | Council Nominee Industrialist Vice Chairman,UPL Group of Companies |\n| Prof. Dinesh K. Gupta | Council Nominee Academicia", "metadata": {"doc": "administration_board-of-governors.md", "url": "https://iitjammu.ac.in/board-of-governors", "title": "Board-Of-Governors", "chunk_idx": 0, "chunk_strategy": "single_chunk", "chunk_meta": {"strategy": "single_chunk"}}}, {"id": "chunk_administration_bogchairman.md_0", "type": "chunk", "department": "administration", "text": "# Page Title: IIT Jammu BOG Chairman - Governance & Leadership\n\n### !Image\n\nAdministration\n\n- Board of Governors\n- BOG Chairman\n- Director\n- Building and Works (B&WC)\n- Deans and Associate Deans\n- Senate\n- Registrar\n- Annual Action Plan Committee\n- Finance Committee\n- Organizational Chart\n\n### **Dr. Sharad Kumar Saraf**\n\n#### **BOG Chairman, IIT Jammu**\n\n## Message for Students of IIT Jammu\n\nProvidence has chosen you to attend this temple of learning. It is now for you to convert learning into knowledge and knowledge into wisdom. When you go out of these hallowed portals be the leader of change, and force of impact on the society\n\nPersonal Webpage - http://www.sksaraf.com/", "metadata": {"doc": "administration_bogchairman.md", "url": "https://iitjammu.ac.in/bogchairman", "title": "Bogchairman", "chunk_idx": 0, "chunk_strategy": "single_chunk", "chunk_meta": {"strategy": "single_chunk"}}}, {"id": "chunk_administration_building-and-works-bwc.md_0", "type": "chunk", "department": "administration", "text": "# Page Title: Indian Institute of Technology Jammu | Leading Engineering Institute for Future Innovators\n\n### !Image\n\nAdministration\n\n- Board of Governors\n- BOG Chairman\n- Director\n- Building and Works (B&WC)\n- Deans and Associate Deans\n- Senate\n- Registrar\n- Annual Action Plan Committee\n- Finance Committee\n- Organizational Chart\n\n## Building and Works (B&WC)\n\n| Name | Designation |\n| --- | --- |\n| Prof. Manoj Singh Gaur, Director | Director |\n| Prof. S. N. Singh | Member |\n| Er. K. N. Rai | Member |\n| Mr. Sarvagya Srivastava | Member |\n| Prof. Anurag Misra | Member |\n| Mr. Pushpak Pandit | Special Invitee |\n| Mr Gian Chand Modgil | Special Invitee |\n| Col Virinder Singh Jeji (Retd.), Registrar | Registrar & Secretary |", "metadata": {"doc": "administration_building-and-works-bwc.md", "url": "https://iitjammu.ac.in/building-and-works-bwc", "title": "Building-And-Works-Bwc", "chunk_idx": 0, "chunk_strategy": "single_chunk", "chunk_meta": {"strategy": "single_chunk"}}}, {"id": "chunk_administration_deans-and-associate-deans.md_0", "type": "chunk", "department": "administration", "text": "# Page Title: Indian Institute of Technology Jammu | Leading Engineering Institute for Future Innovators\n\n- Deans\n- Associate Deans\n\n- !Image\n\n#### DEANS #######\n\n#### Ankit Kathuria\n\nDean (Alumni, Corporate Relations and MoUs)\n\ndean [DOT] alumni [AT] iitjammu [DOT] ac [DOT] in\n\nPROFILE\n- !Image\n\n#### Anup Shukla\n\nDean (Student Affairs)\n\ndean [DOT] sw [AT] iitjammu [DOT] ac [DOT] in\n\nPROFILE\n- !Image\n\n#### Anurag Misra\n\nDean (Infrastructure, Planning & Management)\n\ndean [DOT] ipm [AT] iitjammu [DOT] ac [DOT] in\n\nPROFILE\n- !Image\n\n#### Bacham Eswar Reddy\n\nDean (Faculty Affairs and Administration and Operations)\n\ndean [DOT] faculty [AT] iitjammu [DOT] ac [DOT] in\n\nPROFILE\n- !Image\n\n#### Badri Narayan Subudhi\n\nDean (Digital Infrastructure)\n\ndean [DOT] di [AT] iitjammu [DOT] ac [DOT] in\n\nPROFILE\n- !Image\n\n#### Durai Prabhakaran R T\n\nDean (Research and Consultancy)\n\ndean [DOT] rnc [AT] iitjammu [DOT] ac [DOT] in\n\nPROFILE\n- !Image\n\n#### Goutam Dutta\n\nDean (Strategy and Institute Development)", "metadata": {"doc": "administration_deans-and-associate-deans.md", "url": "https://iitjammu.ac.in/deans-and-associate-deans", "title": "Deans-And-Associate-Deans", "chunk_idx": 0, "chunk_strategy": "repeated_heading_records", "chunk_meta": {"strategy": "repeated_heading_records", "record_heading_level": 4, "record_count": 42}}}, {"id": "chunk_administration_deans-and-associate-deans.md_1", "type": "chunk", "department": "administration", "text": "#### Pratik Kumar\n\nMedia, Website and PR Cell and Waste Water and Solid Waste Management\n\nPROFILE\n- !Image\n\n#### Rajkumar V\n\nSkill Development Programs and CES\n\nPROFILE\n- !Image\n\n#### Roshan Udaram Patil\n\nOnline Education\n\nPROFILE\n- !Image\n\n#### S. R. K. Chaitanya Indukuri\n\nResearch and Projects\n\nPROFILE\n- !Image\n\n#### Sameer Kumar Sarma Pachalla\n\nOutreach\n\nPROFILE\n- !Image\n\n#### Santhilal Subhash\n\nData Centre and operation and management\n\nPROFILE\n- !Image\n\n#### Sarada Prasad Gochhayat\n\nAutomation and Networks\n\nPROFILE\n- !Image\n\n#### Shiva S\n\nSports and Wellness\n\nPROFILE\n- !Image\n\n#### Srishilan C\n\nBudget and Inventory Control\n\nPROFILE\n- !Image\n\n#### Suman Sarkar\n\nSoftware Development (EGS(SARAL)), Institute Software and Portal\n\nPROFILE\n- !Image\n\n#### Vinay Sharma\n\nCorporate Relations\n\nPROFILE\n- !Image\n\n#### Vinit Jakhetiya\n\nCDS\n\nPROFILE\n- !Image\n\n#### Yogesh Madhukarrao Nimdeo\n\nHostel Affairs\n\nPROFILE", "metadata": {"doc": "administration_deans-and-associate-deans.md", "url": "https://iitjammu.ac.in/deans-and-associate-deans", "title": "Deans-And-Associate-Deans", "chunk_idx": 1, "chunk_strategy": "repeated_heading_records", "chunk_meta": {"strategy": "repeated_heading_records", "record_heading_level": 4, "record_count": 42}}}, {"id": "chunk_administration_director.md_0", "type": "chunk", "department": "administration", "text": "# Page Title: IIT Jammu Director - Leadership & Vision\n\n### !Image\n\nAdministration\n\n- Board of Governors\n- BOG Chairman\n- Director\n- Building and Works (B&WC)\n- Deans and Associate Deans\n- Senate\n- Registrar\n- Annual Action Plan Committee\n- Finance Committee\n- Organizational Chart\n\n## Manoj Singh Gaur\n\n#### Director, IIT Jammu\n\nProf Manoj Singh Gaur has been serving as the founding director of the Indian Institute of Technology Jammu since June 2017 and is also a Professor at the Department of Computer Science & Engineering; he is now in his second term.\n\nBefore joining IIT Jammu, he was a Professor and Head of the Department of Computer Science and Engineering at Malaviya National Institute of Technology (MNIT) Jaipur, India. Prof Gaur has also been Dean of Students Affairs and Head of the Central Computer Centre at MNIT Jaipur. He also served as Professor-in-Charge (Coordinator) of IIIT Kota.\n\nIn his teaching and research career of almost three decades, he has been an investigator of", "metadata": {"doc": "administration_director.md", "url": "https://iitjammu.ac.in/director", "title": "Director", "chunk_idx": 0, "chunk_strategy": "single_chunk", "chunk_meta": {"strategy": "single_chunk"}}}, {"id": "chunk_administration_finance-committee.md_0", "type": "chunk", "department": "administration", "text": "# Page Title: Indian Institute of Technology Jammu | Leading Engineering Institute for Future Innovators\n\n### !Image\n\nAdministration\n\n- Board of Governors\n- BOG Chairman\n- Director\n- Building and Works (B&WC)\n- Deans and Associate Deans\n- Senate\n- Registrar\n- Annual Action Plan Committee\n- Finance Committee\n- Organizational Chart\n\n## Finance Committee\n\n| Name | Designation |\n| --- | --- |\n| Dr. Sharad Kumar Saraf | Chairman & Managing Director Technocraft Group of Industries, Mumbai |\n| Ms. Saumya Gupta | Nominee of Central Govt. (Ex-Officio) Joint Secretary [TE] Ministry of Education, New Delhi |\n| Sh. Sanjog Kapoor | Nominee of Central Govt. (Ex-Officio) Joint Secretary & Financial Advisor Ministry of Education, New Delhi |\n| Prof. Sudarshan Kumar | BOG Nominee Academician Deptt. of Aerospace Engineering, IIT Bombay |\n| Prof. S.K. Koul | BOG Nominee CARE, IIT Delhi |\n| Prof. S.V.D. Nageswara Rao | SOM , IIT Bombay |\n| Prof. S.N. Singh | Emeritus Professor Dept. of Applied Mechanics, ", "metadata": {"doc": "administration_finance-committee.md", "url": "https://iitjammu.ac.in/finance-committee", "title": "Finance-Committee", "chunk_idx": 0, "chunk_strategy": "single_chunk", "chunk_meta": {"strategy": "single_chunk"}}}, {"id": "chunk_administration_member-senate-academic-council.md_0", "type": "chunk", "department": "administration", "text": "# Page Title: Indian Institute of Technology Jammu | Leading Engineering Institute for Future Innovators\n\n### !Image\n\nAdministration\n\n- Board of Governors\n- BOG Chairman\n- Director\n- Building and Works (B&WC)\n- Deans and Associate Deans\n- Senate\n- Registrar\n- Annual Action Plan Committee\n- Finance Committee\n- Organizational Chart\n\n## Senate\n\n| Name | Designation |\n| --- | --- |\n| Prof. Manoj Singh Gaur, Director IIT Jammu | Chairman |\n| Dean (Faculty Affairs, Education and Outreach) | Member |\n| Dean (Infrastructure, Planning & Management) | Member |\n| Dean (International Relations) | Member |\n| Dean (Research and Consultancy) | Member |\n| Dean (Strategy and Institute Development) | Member |\n| Dean (Academic Programs) | Member |\n| Dean (Digital Infrastructure) | Member |\n| Dean (Administrative Affairs) | Member |\n| Dean (Alumni and Corporate Relations) | Member |\n| Dean (Student Affairs) | Member |\n| Prof. Ch. Subrahmanyam, Department of Chemistry, IIT Hyderabad | Member |\n| Prof. Amit", "metadata": {"doc": "administration_member-senate-academic-council.md", "url": "https://iitjammu.ac.in/member-senate-academic-council", "title": "Member-Senate-Academic-Council", "chunk_idx": 0, "chunk_strategy": "single_chunk", "chunk_meta": {"strategy": "single_chunk"}}}, {"id": "chunk_administration_nirf_2026_NIRF2026_IITJammu.pdf.md_0", "type": "chunk", "department": "administration", "text": "# Content Flags: short-markdown\n\nNo readable content was extracted from the binary file.", "metadata": {"doc": "administration_nirf_2026_NIRF2026_IITJammu.pdf.md", "url": "ht